Plover Emoji
============

Convert written text to an emoji with a stroke.

Usage
-----

Create a dictionary entry to trigger emoji conversion:

.. code:: json

    {
        "PHOEPBLG": "{:emoji}"
    }

Then write your favorite emoji's name, hit your stroke, and ğŸ’¥!

